                    <h5>üîÑ Real-time Replication</h5>
                    <p>Continuous data flow between Kafka clusters with minimal latency</p>
                </div>
                <div class="key-point">
                    <h5>üìã Schema Synchronization</h5>
                    <p>Automatic Avro Schema Registry replication and versioning</p>
                </div>
                <div class="key-point">
                    <h5>üìç Offset Management</h5>
                    <p>Consumer group offset synchronization for seamless failover</p>
                </div>
                <div class="key-point">
                    <h5>‚öôÔ∏è Auto Topic Creation</h5>
                    <p>Automatic topic and partition management across clusters</p>
