            <div class="slide-number">9</div>
            <h1>EEB Team Implementation Tasks</h1>
            <h2>Technical Configuration Steps</h2>

            <h3>1. Topic Configuration</h3>
            <div class="yaml-block">
Source Topics: 
  - customer-events
  - transaction-logs
  - order-updates
  
Target Topics (with prefix):
  - dev.customer-events
  - dev.transaction-logs  
  - dev.order-updates
            </div>

            <h3>2. MirrorMaker Properties</h3>
            <div class="code-block">
# Core replication settings
source->target.enabled = true
source->target.topics = .*
source->target.replication.factor = 3

# Performance optimization
producer.batch.size = 16384
consumer.max.poll.records = 5000
compression.type = snappy
            </div>

            <h3>3. Security Configuration</h3>
