            <h3>Security Standards</h3>
            <div class="yaml-block">
Authentication:
  - mTLS for Kafka clusters
  - SASL/SCRAM for Schema Registry
  - Certificate rotation every 90 days
  
Authorization:
  - Topic-level ACLs
  - Consumer group permissions
  - Least privilege access
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Slide 11: Monitoring -->
        <div class="slide">
            <div class="slide-number">11</div>
            <h1>Monitoring & Observability</h1>
            <h2>Key Performance Metrics</h2>

            <h3>Replication Health</h3>
            <div class="yaml-block">
Critical Metrics:
  - kafka.connect.mirror.source.record.count
  - kafka.connect.mirror.source.record.rate  
  - kafka.consumer.lag.max
  - kafka.connect.connector.task.status

Performance Metrics:
  - Replication latency (target: < 5 seconds)
  - Throughput rate (messages/second)
  - Error rate (target: < 0.1%)
            </div>

            <h3>Alert Thresholds</h3>
            <div class="key-points">
                <div class="critical-box">
                    <strong>üî¥ Critical Alerts:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Replication lag > 1,000 messages</li>
                        <li>Connector task failures > 0</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="warning-box">
                    <strong>üü° Warning Alerts:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Replication lag > 100 messages</li>
                        <li>High error rate > 1%</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="highlight-box">
                <h4>üìä Monitoring Dashboard Features</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Real-time replication status</li>
                    <li>Topic-level lag monitoring</li>
                    <li>Error tracking and alerting</li>
                    <li>Resource utilization metrics</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Slide 12: Troubleshooting -->
        <div class="slide">
            <div class="slide-number">12</div>
            <h1>Troubleshooting Common Issues</h1>
            <h2>Issue Resolution Guide</h2>

            <div class="two-column">
                <div>
                    <h3>1. Replication Lag</h3>
                    <div class="yaml-block">
Symptoms: Target topics behind source
Diagnosis:
  - Check consumer lag metrics
  - Monitor network connectivity
  - Review connector configuration
Solutions:
  - Increase max.poll.records
  - Scale Kafka Connect cluster
  - Optimize network bandwidth
                    </div>

                    <h3>2. Authentication Failures</h3>
                    <div class="yaml-block">
Symptoms: SSL/SASL errors in logs
Solutions:
  - Verify certificate validity
  - Update credential references
  - Review ACL permissions
  - Check schema registry access
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3>3. Topic Creation Issues</h3>
                    <div class="yaml-block">
Symptoms: Missing target topics
Solutions:
  - Grant topic creation ACLs
  - Update topic regex patterns
  - Manual topic pre-creation
  - Review auto-create settings
                    </div>

                    <h3>4. Schema Registry Sync</h3>
                    <div class="yaml-block">
Symptoms: Schema evolution errors
Solutions:
  - Compare schema versions
  - Update compatibility settings
  - Manual schema registration
  - Review evolution process
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

